AJLK-10 EMBROIDERED POLY CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Poly Chiffon Trouser: Malai Dupatta: Poly Net Fabric composition: Blended Color: Ferozi

This enchanting sky blue ensemble, adorned with delicate embroidery, exudes a serene elegance. The intricately embroidered gharara adds a traditional yet playful touch, making the outfit stand out. Paired with a matching dupatta, this set is perfect for the kids who want to dress up in a festive spirit with their formal attire.
